~ start

I.. I am writing this to any unfortunate soul who may find themselves in this sewer. Escape while you still have time. This place is a prison. There's no way to get out. Nuclear war has thrown the world into chaos and civilization is gone. 

The government has been overthrown and turned corrupt. They've created mutant creatures that eat people alive. Don't even get me started on those maniacal drones. Here, in the sewers, they were easy to kill. Probably damaged by those creatures. But outside? I don't even want to think about it.
Bombs, saws and traps were placed by the army and by bandits. However, outside there are better weapons and better allies.
I think I'll die here. I look crazy, writing notes to some imaginary person who might read this. What has happened to this world.. God save us all.

=> END